summary: An Ordinance authorizing the Mayor and City Comptroller to issue Local Improvement Bonds for the improvement of First Avenue South from the north line of Stacy Street to a point 240' south of Hanford Street in the City of Seattle by filling under Ordinance No. 20324 creating Local Improvement District No. 1960 prescribing the rate of interest thereon and authorizing their delivery to the contractor constructing the improvement.
